@startuml greetup_event_flow

title Greetup - Fluxo Principal de Eventos

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 8
skinparam defaultFontName Arial

actor "Gerente" as GE
participant "App Cliente" as AC
participant "API REST" as API
database "PostgreSQL" as PG
participant "Event Publisher" as PUB
queue "Redis Pub/Sub" as REDIS
participant "Event Subscriber" as SUB
participant "WebSocket Gateway" as WSG
participant "App Prestador" as AP

== Criação do pedido ==

GE -> AC : cria pedido
AC -> API : POST /orders
API -> PG : persiste pedido
PG --> API : pedido criado

API -> PUB : publish(order:created)
PUB -> REDIS : order:created

API --> AC : HTTP 201

== Entrega assíncrona ==

REDIS -> SUB : evento order:created
SUB -> WSG : encaminha evento
WSG -> AP : novo pedido em tempo real

@enduml